<body>
<div class="nav-ticket"><a href="会员中心-成长值策略.html">成长值策略</a> <i>></i> 消费激励策略模型</div>
<form class="layui-form" action="">
    <div class="s-step">
        <h1> 消费<input type="checkbox" name="close" lay-skin="switch" lay-text="" ></h1>
        <div class="b-box">
            <div class="c-box">
                <i class="red">*</i>基本规则：每消费满<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input">元，加<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="">成长值
            </div>
            <div class="c-box" style="margin-left: 12px">
                额外奖励规则：一次性消费满<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input">元，额外加<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="">成长值
                <button class="layui-btn add-btn">添加</button><font style="color: #999">最多添加5个，奖励间不叠加</font>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="s-step">
        <h1> 消费<input type="checkbox" name="close" lay-skin="switch" lay-text="" ></h1>
        <div class="b-box">
            <div class="c-box">
                <i class="red">*</i>基本规则：每消费满<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input">元，加<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="">成长值
            </div>
            <div class="c-box" style="margin-left: 12px">
                额外奖励规则：一次性消费满<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input">元，额外加<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="">成长值
                <button class="layui-btn add-btn">添加</button><font style="color: #999">最多添加5个，奖励间不叠加</font>
            </div>
            <div class="c-box" style="margin-left: 12px">
                额外奖励规则：一次性消费满<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input">元，额外加<input type="text" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="">成长值
                <button class="del-btn">删除</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layui-form-item">
        <div class="layui-input-block" style="margin-right: 130px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px">
            <button type="reset" class="layui-btn layui-btn-primary">取消</button>
            <button class="layui-btn" lay-submit="" lay-filter="demo1">保存</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
<script src="./plugins/layui/layui.js"></script>
<script src="build/js/x-layui.js"></script>
<script src="./build/js/jquery.js"></script>
